{"tid":427231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［美食在民間］勇士中鋒McGee盛讚「康師傅泡麵」賜他力量","createTime":"2017-10-07T10:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T12:52:42.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc278ddddae1b01a7d3a9977b26b587bbc7dd79","tid":427231,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"〔體育中心／綜合報導〕金州勇士與灰狼近期到中國參加NBA季前海外熱身賽，「天兵」中鋒麥基（JaVale McGee）在推特上PO照，大啖「康師傅泡麵」，引起網友們熱議。<br />\n康師傅是NBA中國賽的贊助廠商，麥基除了在推特上PO照吃康師傅泡麵外，還在社群媒體微博上寫到，「這神奇的中國麵幫助我補充能量。」他說，「我現在充滿活力，準備好要打10月8日的上海賽，我可愛的粉絲們，我不要其他禮物，只要這個。」<br />\n麥基今年休賽季以一年短約續留勇士，他上季在勇士例行賽出賽77場，平均上場9.6分鐘可拿場均6.1分、3.2籃板，命中率達65.2％，並在中鋒帕丘利亞（Zaza Pachulia）缺陣時頂上他的位置，季後賽也有不錯表現。<br />\n<a href=\"http://sports.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2216295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2216295&d=1egFhdo94ZcAly336djUoS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5c575e1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2216295&h=350cd81e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sports.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2216295</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/184209_d91cc08fcf5ff714d9483b2215f68e49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F184209_d91cc08fcf5ff714d9483b2215f68e49.jpg&h=2a8e38e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國杯麵係咪唔入流"},{"pid":"61fcc6bacac401e04c33eef1ecee818c7af1c2f8","tid":427231,"uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:56:58.000Z","msg":"食得多個腦會好似mcgee咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8772e58e6d6194f85385ec94b892304376149aa","tid":427231,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:06:29.000Z","msg":"力架食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5135740ec0db7758188befdf153baf7a6bf91929","